'''華川水壩'''（{{kor|名=南|k=화천댐|漢=華川댐|rm=Hwacheon daem|f=y}}）是[[韓國|韓國]][[江原道_(韓國)|江原道]][[華川郡|華川郡]][[北漢江|北漢江]]的[[水壩|水壩]]，於1944年完工。該水壩蓄水後形成了[[水庫|人工湖]][[破虜湖|破虜湖]]。<ref>{{Cite web|script-title=ja:中国、韓国政府に「破虜湖」の名称変更を求める|url=http://www.chosunonline.com/m/svc/article.html?contid=2019052880078|website=www.chosunonline.com|accessdate=2019-05-28|publisher=朝鮮日報|archive-date=2020-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121055901/http://www.chosunonline.com/common/m_login.html?contid=2019052880078&code=news|dead-url=no}}</ref>該水壩在[[朝鲜战争|朝鲜战争]]中成為[[空襲|空襲]]目標，同時用於防範[[朝鮮民主主義人民共和國|朝鮮民主主義人民共和國]]突然釋放{{link-ko|任南水壩|임남댐}}的洪水。

水壩建於[[第二次世界大戰|第二次世界大戰]]時，由[[朝鮮日治時期|朝鮮日治時期]]的[[日本人|日本人]]建造。1939年7月漢江水力電氣株式會社啟動建設，1944年10月完工。首個發電機於5月啟動，10月第二發電機啟動。<ref name=plants/><ref name=local>{{cite web|title=Hwacheon Dam|url=http://tour.ihc.go.kr/tour/tour_view.asp?menu=tour&submenu=main&paramidx=TL0000039|publisher=Hawcheon-gun|accessdate=2011-08-05|language=ko|archive-date=2012-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120328131540/http://tour.ihc.go.kr/tour/tour_view.asp?menu=tour&submenu=main&paramidx=TL0000039|dead-url=no}}</ref>第三發電機於1957年啟動，最後的第四發電機於1968年啟動。在上流的{{link-ko|和平水壩|평화의 댐}}2005年完工以前，一直起着朝鮮任南水壩崩塌或過度[[泄洪|泄洪]]時的第一線防御機能。<ref>{{cite book|last=Hyŏn|first=In-tʻaek|title=The environmental dimension of Asian security: conflict and cooperation over energy, resources, and pollution|year=2007|publisher=US Institute of Peace Press|isbn=1929223730|pages=196–197|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=qVciKjS6C44C&pg=PA196&dq=Hwacheon+Dam+Peace+Dam&hl=en&ei=rEY7TrCCH4mKmQXf_6HUAg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CC4Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Hwacheon%20Dam%20Peace%20Dam&f=false|coauthors=Miranda Alice Schreurs|accessdate=2011-08-05}}</ref>

== 朝鮮戰爭 ==
1951年4月8日深夜，[[朝鲜人民军|朝鲜人民军]]與[[中国人民志愿军|中国人民志愿军]]利用水壩的[[溢洪道|溢洪道]]超量泄洪至下游，導致[[联合国军|联合国军]]5座浮橋無法使用。<ref>{{cite book|last=Gleick|first=Peter H.|title=The world's water: the biennial report on freshwater resources|year=2000|publisher=Island Press|isbn=1559637927|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=b61zOkAs5NcC&pg=PA185&dq=Hwachon+dam+meter&hl=en&ei=tjI7TqjRKYmJmQWStrWCAw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CDEQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q&f=false|coauthors=Pacific Institute for Studies in Development, Environment, and Security|accessdate=2011-08-05|page=185|archive-date=2014-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101160126/http://books.google.com/books?id=b61zOkAs5NcC&pg=PA185&dq=Hwachon+dam+meter&hl=en&ei=tjI7TqjRKYmJmQWStrWCAw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CDEQ6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>4月9日，在该地区完成其他任务的[[美國陸軍第7騎兵團|美國陸軍第7騎兵團]]受命攻占水坝，但因遭到頑強抵抗而失敗。<ref>{{cite book|last=Daily|first=Edward L.|title="Skirmish" red, white and blue: the history of the 7th U.S. Cavalry, 1945–1953|year=1992|publisher=Turner Publishing Company|isbn=1563110881|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=eOxdB02xqxgC&pg=PA96&dq=Hwachon+dam+attack&hl=en&ei=fDU7TvOyL8jMmAXtjunnAg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCwQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Hwachon%20dam%20attack&f=false|accessdate=2011-08-05|pages=96–98|archive-date=2014-01-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140101160135/http://books.google.com/books?id=eOxdB02xqxgC&pg=PA96&dq=Hwachon+dam+attack&hl=en&ei=fDU7TvOyL8jMmAXtjunnAg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCwQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Hwachon%20dam%20attack&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Jr|first=Donald W. Boose|title=Over the beach : US Army amphibious operations in the Korean War|year=2008|publisher=Combat Studies Institute Press|location=Fort Leavenworth, Kan.|isbn=0980123674|pages=271–275|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=HGlEGF2O8z0C&pg=PA271&dq=hwachon+dam+operation+dauntless&hl=en&ei=SF07TruNF-STmQWXpKndAg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=6&ved=0CEYQ6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q&f=false|access-date=2020-11-19|archive-date=2014-04-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140416000746/http://books.google.com/books?id=HGlEGF2O8z0C&pg=PA271&dq=hwachon+dam+operation+dauntless&hl=en&ei=SF07TruNF-STmQWXpKndAg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=6&ved=0CEYQ6AEwBQ#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>4月16日至21日，美軍一度攻占了水壩，但未来得及破坏排水闸即遭志願軍逆襲擊退。美军的[[B-29超級堡壘轟炸機|B-29]]也未能破坏水壩功能，之后在4月30日[[A-1攻擊機|天襲者]]投下{{link-en|Tiny Tim (火箭彈)|Tiny Tim (rocket)|Tiny Tim空對地反艦火箭彈}}與2枚2000磅炸彈，炸開溢洪道[[閘門|閘門]]一個洞。<ref>{{cite book|last=Edwards|first=Paul M.|title=Korean War almanac|year=2006|publisher=Facts On File|location=New York|isbn=0816060371|pages=191–200|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=5gYCm0bM68sC&pg=PA192&dq=Hwa+chon+Dam+capture&hl=en&ei=SGA7TtX7MuLbmAWWzJTRAg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CC4Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Hwa%20chon%20Dam%20capture&f=false|edition=1. ed.|access-date=2020-11-19|archive-date=2014-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140414211853/http://books.google.com/books?id=5gYCm0bM68sC&pg=PA192&dq=Hwa+chon+Dam+capture&hl=en&ei=SGA7TtX7MuLbmAWWzJTRAg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CC4Q6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=Hwa%20chon%20Dam%20capture&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>5月2日，19航空群12架[[F4U海盜式戰鬥機|F4U海盜式戰鬥機]]護航下，8架裝有[[Mk_13型魚雷|Mk 13型魚雷]]的天襲者出擊，發射8枚魚雷，當中7枚命中水壩，6枚爆炸。此攻擊破壞了其中一個[[水閘|水閘]]，并对其他的水闸造成了损伤，从而降低了该水坝制造洪水的能力。<ref>{{cite book|last=Hallion|first=Richard P.|title=The naval air war in Korea|year=2011|publisher=University of Alabama Press|location=Tuscaloosa|isbn=0817356584|pages=120–122|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=TLVnjOU1lf4C&pg=PA121&dq=Hwachon+dam+attack&hl=en&ei=fDU7TvOyL8jMmAXtjunnAg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=5&ved=0CEIQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=Hwachon%20dam%20attack&f=false|access-date=2020-11-19|archive-date=2014-04-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140408142849/http://books.google.com/books?id=TLVnjOU1lf4C&pg=PA121&dq=Hwachon+dam+attack&hl=en&ei=fDU7TvOyL8jMmAXtjunnAg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=5&ved=0CEIQ6AEwBA#v=onepage&q=Hwachon%20dam%20attack&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>其中一隊參與任務的美國海軍飛行中隊VFA-195由「猛虎」改名為「水壩剋星」。<ref name=such>{{cite book|last=Sears|first=David|title=Such men as these : the story of the Navy pilots who flew the deadly skies over Korea|year=2010|publisher=Da Capo Press|location=Cambridge, MA|isbn=0306818515|pages=164|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=J_mTyQcDju0C&pg=PA160&dq=Hwachon+dam+attack&hl=en&ei=fDU7TvOyL8jMmAXtjunnAg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CD0Q6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=Hwachon%20dam%20attack&f=false|access-date=2020-11-19|archive-date=2014-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413095651/http://books.google.com/books?id=J_mTyQcDju0C&pg=PA160&dq=Hwachon+dam+attack&hl=en&ei=fDU7TvOyL8jMmAXtjunnAg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=4&ved=0CD0Q6AEwAw#v=onepage&q=Hwachon%20dam%20attack&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>此攻擊是世界上最後一次以航空魚雷攻擊地面目標的作戰，也是朝鮮戰爭中唯一一次使用魚雷。<ref>{{cite book|last=Polmar|first=Norman|title=One hundred years of world military aircraft|year=2004|publisher=Naval Institute Press|location=Annapolis, MD|isbn=1591146860|pages=293|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=YlHDyi87AQYC&pg=PA293&dq=hwachon+dam+surface+target&hl=en&ei=eX47TsCcNu7OmAXN-LnxAg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CC0Q6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=hwachon%20dam%20surface%20target&f=false|coauthors=Bell, Dana|access-date=2020-11-19|archive-date=2014-04-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140413235016/http://books.google.com/books?id=YlHDyi87AQYC&pg=PA293&dq=hwachon+dam+surface+target&hl=en&ei=eX47TsCcNu7OmAXN-LnxAg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=2&ved=0CC0Q6AEwAQ#v=onepage&q=hwachon%20dam%20surface%20target&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Thompson|first=Robert F. Dorr, Warren|title=Korean air war|year=2003|publisher=Motorbooks International|location=St. Paul, MN|isbn=0760315116|pages=75|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=bvyEpFNGIbcC&pg=PA75&dq=aerial+torpedo+in+the+korean+war&hl=en&ei=iKU7TpKbMMPRmAWX7t3zAg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCwQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q&f=false|access-date=2020-11-19|archive-date=2014-04-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140411171101/http://books.google.com/books?id=bvyEpFNGIbcC&pg=PA75&dq=aerial+torpedo+in+the+korean+war&hl=en&ei=iKU7TpKbMMPRmAWX7t3zAg&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCwQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=The War Stabilizes, 25 January – 30 June 1951|url=http://www.history.navy.mil/photos/events/kowar/51-stab/51-stab.htm|publisher=Department of The Navy – Naval Historical Center|accessdate=2011-08-05|archive-date=2012-01-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120127212752/http://www.history.navy.mil/photos/events/kowar/51-stab/51-stab.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Hearn|first=Chester G.|title=Carriers in combat : the air war at sea|year=2007|publisher=Stackpole Books|location=Mechanicsburg, PA|isbn=081173398X|pages=239|url=http://books.google.com/books?id=sg8ivuKMD5cC&pg=PA239&dq=torpedoes+in+the+korean+war&hl=en&ei=Q6Q7TorQOMmImQXcmYGDAw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCkQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=torpedoes%20in%20the%20korean%20war&f=false|access-date=2020-11-19|archive-date=2014-04-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140415001524/http://books.google.com/books?id=sg8ivuKMD5cC&pg=PA239&dq=torpedoes+in+the+korean+war&hl=en&ei=Q6Q7TorQOMmImQXcmYGDAw&sa=X&oi=book_result&ct=result&resnum=1&ved=0CCkQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=torpedoes%20in%20the%20korean%20war&f=false|dead-url=no}}</ref>

=== 水壩湖 ===
1951年5月26日起4日間水壩附近，[[韓國國軍|韓國國軍]]第6師團與中國人民志願軍交戰，有指志願軍死亡超過2萬人。韓國側將志願軍士兵遺體以重型機器推入水壩湖中進行[[水葬|水葬]]，有指湖水因此變成紅色。戰後，時任總統[[李承晚|李承晚]]訪問水壩湖之際以「擊破蠻虜」命名為[[破虜湖|破虜湖]]。至今仍然有其揮筆的[[紀念碑|紀念碑]]。湖的名字在2010年代引起到訪的中國大陸遊客不滿，計劃恢復破虜湖以前的名稱大鵬湖<ref>{{Cite web |date=2019-05-28 |url=http://www.chosunonline.com/svc/auth/index_login.html?contid=2019052880084&code=news |script-title=ja:「破虜湖」改名を推進する韓国政府の無知と事大主義 |publisher=朝鮮日報 |accessdate=2019-06-04 |archive-date=2020-11-21 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201121055915/http://www.chosunonline.com/svc/auth/index_login.html?contid=2019052880084&code=news |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |date=2019-06-11 |url=https://www.sankei.com/premium/news/190611/prm1906110003-n1.html |script-title=ja:「韓国勝利」の証しを消し去る　中国にへつらう文政権に国民は… |publisher=産経新聞 |accessdate=2019-06-11 |archive-date=2019-06-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190611032839/https://www.sankei.com/premium/news/190611/prm1906110003-n1.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 機能 ==
堤高78公尺，堤頂長435公尺的[[重力壩|重力壩]]。<ref name=hight/>流域面積3,901平方公里，總貯水容量10.18億立方公尺。當中有效貯水容量809萬立方公尺，另有213萬立方公尺作為{{link-en|洪水控制|Flood control}}之用。貯水池面積為38.9平方公里。水壩的排水由16道閘門控制，最大排水量為每秒5,428立方公尺。<ref>{{cite journal|last=Kim|first=Taesoon|coauthors=Jun-Haeng Heo and Chang-Sam Jeong|title=Multireservoir system optimization in the Han River basin using multi-objective genetic algorithms|journal=Wiley InterScience|year=2006|volume=20|series=Hydrological Processes|pages=2057–2075|url=http://hydro-eng.yonsei.ac.kr/data_files/MultireservoirsystemoptimizationintheHanRiverbasinusingmilti-objectivegeneticalgorithms.pdf|accessdate=2011-08-05|publisher=John Wiley & Sons, Ltd.|archive-date=2012-03-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120328131509/http://hydro-eng.yonsei.ac.kr/data_files/MultireservoirsystemoptimizationintheHanRiverbasinusingmilti-objectivegeneticalgorithms.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref>發電所位於水壩西南2.5公里山脊上。發電所設有4部27 MW的{{link-ja|水力發電機|水車発電機}}，有效落差74.5公尺。<ref name=plants/><ref name=local/>

